This is a customized version of the original pyZeroconf from 
	http://sourceforge.net/projects/pyzeroconf
with the following patches
	http://sourceforge.net/tracker/index.php?func=detail&aid=1600775&group_id=100909&atid=628622
	http://sourceforge.net/tracker/index.php?func=detail&aid=1174796&group_id=100909&atid=628622

It has also been changed to be single threaded instead of requiring a seperate thread for everything.
